---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us - TOOLKIFY"
  description="Learn about the mission, philosophy, and local-first security of TOOLKIFY, the visual workspace for web utilities."
>
  <section class="max-w-[1280px] w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-12 flex flex-col gap-10 animate-fade-in-up">
    <!-- Breadcrumb & Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate uppercase">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-brand-blue">About Us</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-4xl sm:text-5xl tracking-tight text-primary mt-1">
        About TOOLKIFY
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-slate max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        We believe that online calculators, converters, and diagnostic utility tools don't have to be clinical, boring, or insecure. TOOLKIFY reimagines finance, health, fun, audio, mobile, and developer tools as a tactile, collaborative visual playground.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Grid Content -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
      <!-- Left Content Column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-xl text-primary flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-brand-yellow"></span>
            Our Philosophy: Local-First Security
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Every day, users paste sensitive paycheck details, loan values, database keys, or code scripts into online tools. Most of these sites upload your text to server backends, logging them or running active tracking codes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed font-semibold">
            TOOLKIFY is different. It is 100% serverless.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            All algorithmsâ€”from compound interest math to JSON parsingâ€”run locally inside your browser's V8 sandbox. Zero bytes of your input data are ever transmitted to our servers. Your security is guaranteed by design, not just by a privacy policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-teal-light text-moss-dark flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm select-none">âš¡</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-primary">Microsecond Execution</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Without roundtrips to servers, calculations happen instantly as you type. Real-time calculations update immediately.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-rose-light text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm select-none">ðŸŽ¨</div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-base text-primary">Miro-Inspired Canvas</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Visual sketching and draggable sticky notes let you brainstorm interfaces, map flows, and keep raw text notes side-by-side with calculators.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Feature Column (Pastel Card Accent) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="card-feature-yellow flex flex-col gap-6">
          <span class="badge-tag-yellow bg-yellow-light text-yellow-dark self-start">THE MISSION</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-2xl tracking-tight text-primary">
            Bridging the gap between structure and visual design.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-dark/95 leading-relaxed">
            Web development is visual. User calculations, health benchmarks, audio checks, and diagnostic workflows require builders to jump between templates.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-yellow-dark/95 leading-relaxed">
            TOOLKIFY gathers these disparate workflows into a single workspace, giving teams the exact utilities they need alongside a canvas to organize their thoughts.
          </p>
          <div class="h-[1px] bg-yellow-dark/20 my-2"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-yellow-light border border-yellow-dark/20 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm text-yellow-dark select-none font-display">B</div>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary">TOOLKIFY Core Team</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-yellow-dark/80 font-medium">Built with Astro & Tailwind 4</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- Comprehensive Categories Section -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mt-6">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-2">
        <h2 class="font-display font-medium text-3xl tracking-tight text-primary">
          Our Workspace Tool Capabilities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
          TOOLKIFY features 56 specialized utilities organized into 9 specialized domains. Each workspace is fully client-side and optimized for seamless local performance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- 1. Visual Collaboration Canvas -->
        <div class="card-feature-yellow flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-yellow bg-yellow-light text-yellow-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Collaboration</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸŽ¨</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Visual Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-yellow-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Draggable sticky notes, drawing boards, and flowchart connections layered on a tactile canvas. Perfect for mapping ideas next to active utilities.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-yellow-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-yellow-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Visual Whiteboard</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Sketchpad</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Draggable Canvas</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Developer & Text Utilities -->
        <div class="card-feature-teal flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-purple bg-teal-light text-moss-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Developer</span>
              <span class="text-lg">âš¡</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Developer & Text</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-moss-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Instantly format, parse, validate, and convert coding assets. Designed with 100% sandboxed execution to keep sensitive code scripts safe.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-moss-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-moss-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">JSON Formatter</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Base64 & URL</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Diff Checker</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">UUID & Hash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Financial & Tax Mathematics -->
        <div class="card-feature-yellow flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-yellow bg-yellow-light text-yellow-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Finance & Tax</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸ“ˆ</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Financial & Tax Math</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-yellow-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Calculate loan amortizations, marginal tax brackets, paycheck deductions, and compound interest rates on safe, serverless equations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-yellow-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-yellow-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Mortgage Pay</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Take-Home Pay</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Compound Interest</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Health & Fitness Benchmarks -->
        <div class="card-feature-teal flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-purple bg-teal-light text-moss-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Health</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸƒ</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Health & Fitness</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-moss-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Evaluate physiological profiles, estimate nutritional requirements, calculate body metrics, and track hydration parameters.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-moss-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-moss-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Calorie Deficit</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">BMI Calculator</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Macro Split</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Fun & Cognitive Focus -->
        <div class="card-feature-rose flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-coral bg-rose-light text-primary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Fun</span>
              <span class="text-lg">â±ï¸</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Fun & Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Test user input response times, typing speed velocity, click metrics, and maintain workflow velocity using structured Pomodoro timers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-hairline-strong/20">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Typing Test</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Reaction Time</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Pomodoro Timer</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. Audio & Acoustic Diagnostics -->
        <div class="card-feature-coral flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-coral bg-coral-light text-coral-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Audio</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸ”Š</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Audio & Acoustics</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-coral-dark/95 leading-relaxed">
              Generate precise sound frequencies, test microphone latency outputs, and check stereo system polarities utilizing the Web Audio API.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-coral-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-coral-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-coral-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-coral-dark font-medium">White & Brown Noise</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-coral-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-coral-dark font-medium">Headphone Test</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-coral-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-coral-dark font-medium">Microphone Check</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 7. Mobile Device Diagnostics -->
        <div class="card-feature-rose flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-coral bg-rose-light text-primary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Mobile</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸ“±</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Mobile Telemetry</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
              Read real-time device orientation angles, magnetic fields, light sensor value lux feeds, and geolocation velocities.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-hairline-strong/20">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Bubble Level</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Compass Rose</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-rose-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-primary font-medium">Light Meter</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 8. Display & Hardware Diagnostics -->
        <div class="card-feature-yellow flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-yellow bg-yellow-light text-yellow-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Display</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸ–¥ï¸</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Display & Input</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-yellow-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Perform display Hz speed checks, detect peripheral double-clicks, verify keyboard repeat rates, and audit display configurations.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-yellow-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-yellow-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Refresh Rate (Hz)</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Double-Click Test</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-yellow-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-yellow-dark font-medium">Key Repeat Test</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 9. Everyday Utilities -->
        <div class="card-feature-teal flex flex-col gap-4 p-6 rounded-xxl border border-hairline-soft justify-between">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="badge-tag-purple bg-teal-light text-moss-dark text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Everyday</span>
              <span class="text-lg">ðŸ› ï¸</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">Everyday Utilities</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-moss-dark/90 leading-relaxed">
              Distraction-free calculations for timezone comparisons, solid-color monitor calibrations, and design-focused color extractions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-moss-dark/10">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-semibold text-moss-dark uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">Key Tools:</span>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Time Zone</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Color Picker</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] bg-teal-light/80 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-moss-dark font-medium">Dead Pixel Scan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Milestones/Timeline section -->
    <div class="card-base bg-surface-soft flex flex-col gap-6">
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary text-center">Core Project Milestones</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-blue uppercase">Phase 1 &bull; Core Utilities</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">Local Sandboxed Computations</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Established client-only calculation engines for mortgage models, BMI equations, typing tests, and developer formatters.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-teal uppercase">Phase 2 &bull; Multi-Tier Suite</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">56 Specialized Workspaces</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Expanded catalog across 8 categories including Finance, Health, Audio, Display Diagnostics, and Mobile sensors.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-canvas rounded-xl border border-hairline">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-coral uppercase">Phase 3 &bull; Visual Integration</span>
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-sm text-primary">Tactile Sketchpad Canvas</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Kept whiteboard sketches, note cards, and dynamic connections layered side-by-side with calculators for seamless planning.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

